    <section>
      <title>Changes in Edition 0.7.1</title>

      <para>The following changes were made:</para>

      <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
          <para>Various changes in <xref linkend="flex-dev" /> to support the
          FlexMojos 3.3.0 release:</para>

          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para>Modified <xref linkend="flex-dev-sect-config-build" /> to
              include instructions for referencing Sonatype's Flexmojos
              repository in a project's POM. (<ulink
              url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-260">MVNDEF-260</ulink>
              and <ulink
              url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-263">MVNDEF-263</ulink>)</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Update <xref
              linkend="fig-flex-dev-sonatype-public-proxy" /> to reflect the
              switch to the Sonatype Flexmojos Repository. (<ulink
              url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-264">MVNDEF-264</ulink>)</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para>Update <xref lang=""
              linkend="fig-flex-dev-adding-sonatype-to-group" /> to reflect
              the switch to the Sonatype Flexmojos Repository. (<ulink
              url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-265">MVNDEF-265</ulink>)</para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Updated Maven Version to 2.2.1. (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-268">MVNDEF-268</ulink>)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Moving most introduction examples to the archetype:generate
          goal (instead of archetype:create) (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-41">MVNDEF-41</ulink>)</para>

          <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
              <para><xref linkend="simple-project" /> now introduces the
              <varname>archetype:generate</varname> goal first.
              <varname>archetype:create</varname> is still useful, but
              <varname>archetype:generate</varname> is much friendlier and a
              more appropriate way to introduce new Maven users to the power
              of Maven Archetypes.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para><xref linkend="customizing" /> now uses the
              <varname>archetype:generate</varname> goal instead of
              <varname>archetype:create</varname> goal.</para>
            </listitem>

            <listitem>
              <para><xref linkend="web" /> new uses the archetype:generate
              goal instead of the archetype:create goal.</para>
            </listitem>
          </itemizedlist>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Added <varname>${project.baseUri}</varname> to <xref
          linkend="resource-filtering-sect-project-properties" />. (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-141">MVNDEF-141</ulink>)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Fixed XML element ordering error in <xref
          linkend="ex-customization-attach-assembly" />. (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-32">MVNDEF-32</ulink>)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>A few readers were confused about an example in Chapter 7. A
          clarification was added to <xref
          linkend="multimodule-web-spring-sect-spring-running-web" /> to
          instruct the reader to run <command>mvn clean install</command> from
          the top-level directory before attempting to build the database with
          hbm2ddl. (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-43">MVNDEF-43</ulink>)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Verified that examples can be compiled without the need for
          Sonatype repositories in response to a reader question. (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-72">MVNDEF-72</ulink>)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Minor formatting typo fixed in <xref
          linkend="assemblies-sect-building" />. (<ulink
          url="https://issues.sonatype.org/browse/MVNDEF-42">MVNDEF-42</ulink>)</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Resized all Vector Images to fit within Print Margins.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Resized PDF to Royal Quatro sizing for print-on-demand.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>Automated generation of print figures.</para>
        </listitem>

        <listitem>
          <para>PDF now bundles fonts to satisfy pre-print
          requirements.</para>
        </listitem>
      </itemizedlist>
    </section>
    
